extendedInfo.description: *Doesn't work on your phone? Download LWP Creator then visit my website to download the source images I used for this and other LWPs!Auntie Dot is an A.I. from Halo: Reach. This animation is a loading screen from the game.This method was first used by andrew121. His application, LWP Creator can be found in the market.
